#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/electronic_labels.rst:160
msgid "Select the product you want to apply a discount to."
msgstr "Виберіть продукт, до якого потрібно застосувати знижку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/electronic_labels.rst:162
