#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:20
msgid ""
"Create a QFPay account on the `QFPay website <https://qfpay.global/products/"
"qfpay-pos-api/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Створіть обліковий запис QFPay на `веб-сайті QFPay <https://qfpay.global/"
"products/qfpay-pos-api/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:21
msgid ""
"Request the activation of `Asynchronous Notifications <https://sdk.qfapi.com/"
"docs/common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ from QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Запитайте активацію `Асинхронних сповіщень <https://sdk.qfapi.com/docs/"
"common-api/asynchronous-notification/>`_ у QFPay."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:23
msgid ""
"Provide the Odoo server address to QFPay, followed by `/qfpay/notify`, and "
"copy the notification key provided by QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Надайте QFPay адресу сервера Odoo, після якої вкажіть `/qfpay/notify`, і "
"скопіюйте ключ сповіщення, наданий QFPay."

