msgid ""
"Enable :ref:`Units of Measure & Packagings <inventory/product_replenishment/"
"configuration>` in the Inventory app settings."
msgstr ""
"Увімкніть :ref:`Одиниці виміру та упаковки <inventory/product_replenishment/"
