"поверху в поле :guilabel:`Поверхи` та натисніть `Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:133
msgid "From the POS frontend"
msgstr "З фронтенду Точки продажу"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:135
msgid ""
"To create floors and tables from the frontend, :ref:`open the POS register "
"<pos/use/open-register>`, click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger "
